# Root reference — each stack uses its own .env file next to its docker-compose.
#
# 1) Auth service:        auth/app/.env         (see auth/app/.env.example)
# 2) Jitsi:               jitsi/.env            (see jitsi/.env.production.example and jitsi/env.example)
# 3) Monitoring / Grafana: monitoring/.env       (see monitoring/.env.example)
# 4) Rocket.Chat:         rocketchat/.env       (see rocketchat/.env.example)
#
# Placeholders for documentation (set in the files above, not all in one file):
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
# JWT_SECRET=
# ALLOWED_DOMAIN=
# GRAFANA_ADMIN_PASSWORD=
